    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 (996) Carrera 4S in museum-quality condition. This wide-body specimen features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six, putting power down through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling AWD system. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach: the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a dual-row ceramic upgrade, and the rear main seal (RMS) is completely dry. The cooling system has been overhauled with a low-temperature thermostat and CSF radiators to mitigate heat soak. Suspension kinematics remain factory-tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the precise feedback expected of the 996 chassis. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no evidence of orange peel or paint depth discrepancies, while the cabin's leather remains supple with zero bolster wear or pixel degradation on the instrument cluster. A true turn-key investment for the Porsche purist.",
